data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter1
data.value: Isitatimende of the Prophet (ngamasaha): 'Islam kusekelwe ezimisweni ezinhlanu.'

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter12
data.value: Ukuze abalekele (run away) kusukela Al-Fitan (izilingo futhi afflications njll) iyingxenye yenkolo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter13
data.value: Isitatimende of the Prophet (ngamasaha): 'Ngiyazi Allah (Azza wa jal) abangcono kunawo onke ka uyenze'.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter15
data.value: Emabanga akaphakeme amakholwa izobe ngokwezenzo zabo ezinhle.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter17
data.value: Isitatimende of Allah (Azza wa jal): "Kodwa uma bephenduka futhi enze Iqamat-njengoba-Salat [sipho Salat (imithandazo) ngokuphelele] futhi anikeze Zakat ke ukushiya indlela yabo free."

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter18
data.value: Yilowo nalowo athi ukholo isenzo (izenzo ezinhle).

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter19
data.value: Uma omunye angazamukeli Islam ngempela, kodwa ingabe kunjalo ngokucindezelwa noma ngenxa yokwesaba ukuthi singase wabulala njll

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter22
data.value: Tono ngito kusuka ukungazi isoni akusona disbeliever ngaphandle uma emkhonzayo abanye kanye Allah (Azza wa jal).

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter23
data.value: Isitatimende of Allah (Azza wa jal): { "Uma amaqembu amabili (noma amaqembu) kusukela phakathi amakholwa kuwele ukulwa, khona-ke yenza ukuthula phakathi kwabo bobabili. '} 4,49

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter24
data.value: Zulm (okungalungile) kohlobo olulodwa kungaba elikhulu noma elincane kuka nesinye.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter26
data.value: Ukusungula imithandazo ngobusuku Qadr kuyingxenye yokholo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter27
data.value: Al-Jihad (impi engcwele - silwa imbangela Allah) iyingxenye yokholo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter28
data.value: It is a yingxenye yokholo ukusungula (Nawafil - wokuzithandela) imithandazo ngezikhathi zasebusuku Ramadan.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter29
data.value: Ukuze bagcine Saum [ukudla (ngezimfundiso Islamic)] phakathi nenyanga ka-Ramadan (ngobuqotho nangokwethembeka) ethemba ukuthola imivuzo Allah kuphela, kuyingxenye yokholo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter32
data.value: (Kuthiwani ngokuphathelene ukuphakama) umuntu ehlanganisa Islam ngobuqotho.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter33
data.value: Ad-Din (deed abalungileyo - isenzo sokukhulekela) wayemthanda kakhulu Allah (Azza wa jal) wukuthi okwenziwa njalo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter34
data.value: Ukholo uyanda futhi uya ngokuya lehla.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter36
data.value: Ukuze ihambisane izindwendwe umngcwabo (endaweni angcwatshwa) kuyingxenye yokholo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter37
data.value: Ukwesaba ikholwa ukuze imisebenzi yakhe emihle usesenzé saba yize nesithembiso (elahlekile) ngaphandle kolwazi lwakhe.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter38
data.value: Kubutwa kwemibuto (angel) Jibrael (Gabriel) kusukela uMphrofethi (ngamasaha) mayelana Belief, Islam, Ihsan (ukuphelela).

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter4
data.value: A Muslim nguye ugwema amaSulumane lokulimaza ngolimi nezandla zakhe.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter40
data.value: Ukuphakama ukuthi umuntu ushiya konke ngabazeka (akucacile) izinto ngenxa yenkolo.

data.name: IslamInfo_bukhariBook2Chapter41
data.value: Ukuze akhokhele Al-Khumus (owodwa nanhlanu ngempango yempi ukuba sinikwe udaba Allah) iyingxenye yokholo.

data.value: Lokho okushiwo ngokuqondene ethi: '. Umvuzo wezenzo kuxhomeke inhloso'

data.value: Ukuphinda inkulumo komuntu kathathu ukuze senze abanye baqonde.
